NAVI GAZEBO SIMULATION

install gazebo 5 and gazebo-ros packages:

$ sudo apt-get install ros-indigo-gazebo5-ros
$ sudo apt-get install ros-indigo-gazebo5-ros-control
$ sudo apt-get install ros-indigo-gazebo5-ros-pkgs

Commands you need to run!:
(If you want to use the joystick controller)
$ sudo apt-get install ros-indigo-joy

(Tell Gazebo where to find the building model)
export GAZEBO_MODEL_PATH=~/.../catkin_ws/src/navi_sim_gazebo/models:$GAZEBO_MODEL_PATH
